data.description: Discover this timeless brick ranch home in a prime location! With 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, this home offers comfort and space for all.  Step inside to the spacious living room with hardwood floors and lots of natural light.  Cozy up by the fireplace in winter and enjoy the rest of the year in the 3 Season room, both offer a tranquil retreat to relax and unwind. Entertain effortlessly in the basement's lounge area, complete with a bar for hosting memorable gatherings. Conveniently located near amenities, schools, and parks, this home presents an opportunity not to be missed!
